Class:
/IWBEP/CL_MGW_DATA_UTIL

Methods:
PAGING
FILTERING
ORDERBY

__________________________

Example inside of a Get Entity Set

      CALL METHOD /iwbep/cl_mgw_data_util=>paging
        EXPORTING
          is_paging = is_paging
        CHANGING
          ct_data   = et_entityset.
          
          
      DATA(lt_order) = CORRESPONDING #( io_tech_request_context->get_orderby( ) ).
      "order by
      CALL METHOD /iwbep/cl_mgw_data_util=>orderby
        EXPORTING
          it_order = lt_order
        CHANGING
          ct_data  = et_entityset.          

DATA: lt_filter_tmp TYPE /iwbep/t_mgw_select_option.

lt_filter = it_filter. "TYPE /IWBEP/T_MGW_SELECT_OPTION

      TRY.
          lt_filter_tmp = VALUE #( ( property = lv_abap_field select_options = lt_filter[ 1 ]-select_options ) ) .
        CATCH cx_sy_itab_line_not_found.
      ENDTRY.
      "filter by
      CALL METHOD /iwbep/cl_mgw_data_util=>filtering
        EXPORTING
          it_select_options = lt_filter_tmp
        CHANGING
          ct_data           = ct_table.
